item.description:
@xxbanditxx wrote:

yo dude 1345:

erh in npc.java make sure that the kalphite bosses Hit points and stuff is defined to start off bring an item to the kalphite queen then click on that item and then click on the queen now switch to the cmd that loads the server/runs it and it should say something along the lines of “player used item id #### with npc id ####” now take that npc id and search it and npc.java in the data/cfg folder , define all of the Kalphites stats and if it isn’t on there then copy and paste a random one and put the kalphites npc id on it. It should work now, If not post back =p.
